{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida7924df8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"240i"},"text":"§ 240i.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual report on unfunded priorities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7924df9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In General","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 10 days after the date on which the budget of the President for a fiscal year is submitted to Congress pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":", the Under Secretary of Defense (Comptroller) shall submit to the Secretary of Defense, the Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff, and the congressional defense committees a report on unfunded priorities of the Department of Defense related to audit readiness and remediation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dfa-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Elements","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dfb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Each report under subsection (a) shall include, for each unfunded priority covered by such report, the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dfc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A summary description of such priority, including the objectives to be achieved if such priority were to be funded (whether in whole or in part).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dfd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The additional amount of funds recommended in connection with the objectives identified under subparagraph (A).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dfe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Account information with respect to such priority, including, as applicable, the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida7924dff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/C/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Line item number, in the case of applicable procurement accounts.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e00-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/C/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Program element number, in the case of applicable research, development, test, and evaluation accounts.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e01-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/1/C/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Sub-activity group, in the case of applicable operation and maintenance accounts.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e02-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Under Secretary shall ensure that the unfunded priorities covered by a report under subsection (a) are listed in the order of urgency of priority, as determined by the Under Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e03-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Unfunded Priority Defined","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section, the term “unfunded priority”, with respect to a fiscal year, means an activity related to an audit readiness or remediation effort stemming from a relevant requirement under the Chief Financial Officer Act ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002021"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002021"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/576"},"text":"Public Law 101–576","children":[],"tail":"), chapter 9 of title 31, or this chapter that—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e04-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is not funded in the budget of the President for that fiscal year, as submitted to Congress pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e05-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is necessary to address a shortfall in an audit readiness or remediation activity; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e06-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" would have been recommended for funding through the budget referred to in paragraph (1) if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e07-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" additional resources had been available for the budget to fund the program, activity, or mission requirement; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e08-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s240i/c/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the program, activity, or mission requirement had emerged before the budget was formulated.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida7924e09-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tX/s1005/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title X, § 1005(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/3837"},"text":"134 Stat. 3837","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida7924e0a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida7924e0b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"ida7924e0c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Chief Financial Officer Act, referred to in subsec. (c), probably means the Chief Financial Officers Act of 1990, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/576"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–576","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-15"},"text":"Nov. 15, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/2838"},"text":"104 Stat. 2838","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1990 Amendment note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s501"},"text":"section 501 of Title 31","children":[],"tail":", Money and Finance, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
